lead_paragraph: Any suggestion that Wednesday's EFL Cup showdown between Manchester United and City would lack the usual derby intensity has been removed by the gathering pressure on both managers.

headline.print_headline: Dual Manchester Slump Adds Gravitas to EFL Cup Derby
